message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 – Operating Board Application Guidelines]

𝗝𝗢𝗜𝗡 𝗧𝗛𝗘 𝗦𝗨𝗣𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧! 🛡️

The backbone of every mission is a strong support team—and this is your call to action! Here are the guidelines for non-performing member applications.

🗓️ 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗣𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗼𝗱: September 10–16, 2025 (FORM CLOSES AT 11:59 PM)
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 Step up, bring your strategy, and help assemble a winning team. May your application hit the mark! 🎯

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas
Micaella Alegiojo

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers
